Changes:
 apl (1.8-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=low
 .
   * Portability improved
     GNU APL 1.1 now runs under GNU/Linux, CYGWIN, FreeBSD, and OS-X
 .
   * New memory management using smart pointers
     GNU APL 1.2 uses a new memory management for APL values
 .
   * Native Functions
     GNU APL 1.2 now supports user defined APL functions written in C++
